<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 border-y border-gray-200">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">

    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Common questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center">
          What does "missed-call protection" actually do?
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          When a customer calls and you can't answer, our system sends an instant SMS within seconds. It keeps the conversation going, answers basic questions about your services, and guides them to book an appointment directly in your calendar — automatically, 24/7.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center">
          What's the Revenue Recovery Guarantee?
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          You will see a minimum of 5 recovered leads booked in your calendar within 30 days of going live — or your money back. No conditions, no fine print.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center">
          How fast can I go live?
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          2 weeks from qualification to live system. We handle all setup, integration, and testing.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <a href="/faq" class="text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 font-medium transition">View all FAQ →</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>